"aux"

was  AUX * (^ PASSIVE) = +
	@PAST3SG.

"det"

the  D *  (^ DEF) = +.

The  D *  (^ DEF) = +
	(^ CAPITAL) = +.

A   D *  (^ DEF) = -
	(^ NUM) = sg
	(^ CAPITAL) = +.

a   D *  (^ DEF) = -
	 (^ NUM) = sg.

"Coordination"

and  CONJ * @(COORD-FORM %stem);
     CONJnp * @(COORD-FORM %stem) (^NUM) = pl.

"punctuation"

. PERIOD * (^ STMT-TYPE) = declarative. 

, COMMA  * . 

!        EXCL * (^ STMT-TYPE) = exclamation.

"prep"

by P * @(PREP by).

to P * @(PREP to).

on P * @(PREP on).

in P * @(PREP in).

with P * @(PREP with).

for P * { (^ PRED) = 'for<(^OBJ)>'
          (^ PTYPE) = sem
        |
          (^ PTYPE) = nosem
          (^ PFORM) = for }.

